about.summary: Exploratory graphical analysis of multivariate data, specifically gene expression data with different projection methods: principal component analysis, correspondence analysis, spectral map analysis.

name: r-mpm
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0-22' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mpm
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: mpm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/mpm_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/mpm/mpm_{{ version }}.tar.gz

  sha256: d3ba4053cd57a189cb65c5fa20e6a4152374aead8c985254cb6e550e36e23272

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 1002

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - r-base
    - r-kernsmooth
    - r-mass

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-kernsmooth
    - r-mass

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mpm')"  # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mpm')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://mpm.r-forge.r-project.org
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: 'Exploratory graphical analysis of multivariate data, specifically gene expression
    data with different projection methods: principal component analysis, correspondence
    analysis, spectral map analysis.'

  license_family: GPL3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - dpryan79
    - MathiasHaudgaard
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
